ExtLsdbAge.description: This field is the age of the link state advertisement in seconds.

ExtLsdbChecksum.description: This field is the checksum of the complete contents of the advertisement

ExtLsdbLsid.description: The Link State ID is an LS Type Specific field containing either a Router ID or an IP address; it identifies the piece of the routing domain that is being described by the advertisement.

ExtLsdbRouterId.description: The 32-bit number that uniquely identifies the originating router in the Autonomous System.

ExtLsdbSequence.description: The sequence number field is a signed 32-bit integer.  It starts with the value '80000001'h

ExtLsdbType.description: The type of the link state advertisement. Each link state type has a separate advertisement format.
